            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Apple 為 Snoopy 迷送上聖誕禮物，Apple Watch 錶面和 Apple TV 4K 螢幕保護程式</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/12/apple-snoppy-apple-tv-4k/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-snoppy-apple-tv-4k</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/12/apple-snoppy-apple-tv-4k/life-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[藍骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 06:20:20 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[apple tv]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[apple watch]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[snoopy]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1280920</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>長青的 Snoopy 至今仍然有不少粉絲，而 Apple 最近就宣佈推出一系列 Snoopy 主題新功能，包括 Apple Watch 互動錶面及 Apple TV 4K 螢幕保護程式，作為聖誕禮物。<br /><span id="more-1280920"></span></p><p>Apple 表示，全新的 Apple Watch 錶面以 Snoopy 和 Woodstock 為主角，會與時針互動玩耍，更會根據當地天氣變化作出反應，在用戶運動時更會展現活力十足的動態效果。同時，在 Apple TV 4K（第二代及以後版本）推出的 Snoopy 螢幕保護程式，則以生動的動畫和變化的季節場景呈現，為居家環境增添趣味。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoopyappletv4kscree-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280923" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoopyappletv4kscree-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoopyappletv4kscree-scaled.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoopyappletv4kscree-1-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280924" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoopyappletv4kscree-1-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoopyappletv4kscree-1-scaled.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoopyappletv4kscree-2-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280925" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoopyappletv4kscree-2-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/snoopyappletv4kscree-2-scaled.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>現在 Apple TV+ 作為《Snoopy 花生漫畫》的官方播放平台，有提供多部獲獎的原創作品及經典花生漫畫作品，包括深受歡迎的《查理布朗的大南瓜》、《查理布朗的感恩節》以及《查理布朗的愉快聖誕》等特別節目，讓 Snoopy 迷在聖誕佳節可以在家輕鬆觀賞。</p><p>來源：Apple</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
